  <summary date="2019-08-19T20:11:30Z" status="Introduced in House">Telework Metrics and Cost Savings Act

This bill requires a federal agency's telework policy to include information on the following: (1) annual goals for increasing the telework participation rate, and (2) methods for collecting data related to cost savings achieved through telework.</summary>
